data.description: Step into the epitome of luxurious living with this magnificent 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom pool home, perfectly situated on a corner lot. The property boasts not only a sparkling pool for those warm days but also a relaxing hot tub for the ultimate in outdoor indulgence. The fenced yard ensures privacy and security, creating a serene retreat, and the large screened lanai provides a perfect setting for enjoying the beautiful surroundings.    As you enter the home, you are greeted by an open kitchen adorned with modern elegance. The kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances, creating a stylish and functional space for both casual meals and gourmet cooking. The open layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living areas, making it an ideal space for entertaining friends and family.    The 4 bedrooms are generously sized, offering comfort and tranquility. The main suite, in particular, is a sanctuary with its own private bath and ample closet space. The additional 3.5 baths feature contemporary design and high-end finishes, ensuring both convenience and sophistication.    One of the unique features of this home is the private entrance on one end, catering to the needs of extended family or guests seeking their own space. With no HOA restrictions, the property allows for the freedom to personalize and enjoy the home to its fullest potential.    A dedicated home office or studio space provides the perfect environment for work, creativity, or relaxation. This residence is thoughtfully designed to accommodate the demands of a modern lifestyle while maintaining an atmosphere of warmth and comfort.    The lovely landscaping surrounding the property enhances the overall aesthetic, creating a picture-perfect setting for this remarkable home. Every detail has been considered to ensure that this residence is not just a house, but a haven of luxury, style, and functionality. Welcome to a home where every amenity and feature has been carefully curated to offer the ultimate in comfortable and elegant living.
